Don‚Äôt have to wait for the offseason! We saw the reveal video and decided right then and there to go with the concept for the season.

IHOT Robotics (1414) CAD Release General Forum
[File] We‚Äôve been asked by various teams throughout the season if we would release our CAD, so here it is! Our robot, Encore, was largely inspired by Orbit‚Äôs robot this year. This was a complete redesign as we decided our initial design was too complex for us to manage. You‚Äôll see many similarities, but we‚Äôve also made it our own with quite a few differences in implementation details. We added an ‚Äúamp deflector‚Äù which moves into the path of the note, helping our robot score into the amp withou‚Ä¶
